- [muffled] I can fit it
in my mouth.

06:09.502 --> 06:11.903
Ooh, it tastes
like licorice.

06:11.905 --> 06:14.639
- You idiots!
That goo is dangerous!

06:14.641 --> 06:16.908
Weren't you two morons
listening?

06:16.910 --> 06:19.610
- No, not really.
I drifted off.

06:19.612 --> 06:23.514
- But just look at all
the cool stuff it can do.

06:23.516 --> 06:26.651
You can make a hat...
Or a beard.

06:26.653 --> 06:29.120
- Or an awesome toupee.

06:29.122 --> 06:34.225
- Toupee?
You mean...Hair?

06:34.227 --> 06:35.126
How do I look?

06:35.128 --> 06:38.029
- What is <i>wrong</i>
with you people?

06:38.031 --> 06:40.598
That goo can destroy
everything!

06:40.600 --> 06:41.866
- Seems safe to me.

06:41.868 --> 06:44.702
- That's what they said
about microwave ovens,

06:44.704 --> 06:47.205
Dry cleaning,
and corndogs.

06:47.207 --> 06:48.372
- See ya later, sandy.

06:48.374 --> 06:53.211
- Yeah, these goo bubbles
won't bounce themselves.

06:55.147 --> 06:58.649
- You have been warned.

06:58.651 --> 07:01.986
[surf music]

07:01.988 --> 07:03.187
♪

07:03.189 --> 07:07.191
- Oh, man, where will we get
another ball?

07:07.193 --> 07:10.561
- Why not try
a goo bubble?

07:10.563 --> 07:12.096
- Thanks.

07:12.098 --> 07:14.899
Hey, it sticks like glue.

07:14.901 --> 07:18.903
Go long.

07:20.939 --> 07:22.940
- [laughs]
awesome!

07:22.942 --> 07:24.709
I still got it.

07:24.711 --> 07:27.612
I wish I could swim.

07:27.614 --> 07:30.414
- It's so hot.

07:33.151 --> 07:35.753
Oh, it's so cooling.

07:35.755 --> 07:37.121
Thanks, goo.

07:37.123 --> 07:38.723
- Thanks, goo.

07:38.725 --> 07:40.391
- Thanks, goo.

